  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Infants with congenital heart disease.

          -  Admitted to cardiothoracic unit for either palliative or corrective surgery.

          -  Suffering from nutritional deficiencies with body weights less than 2 SD from mean
             weight for age and sex.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Congenital or acquired anomaly of gastrointestinal tract (i.e. intestinal perforation
             or necrotizing enterocolitis).

          -  Metabolic or endocrine disease or any systemic illness.

          -  Fever or infection within 5 days before the study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
